Package: tcgaR
Title: Interface in R for the TCGA Portal
Version: 0.99.5
Authors@R: c(person("Jean-Philippe", "Fortin", role = c("cre", "aut"),
                    email = "jfortin@jhsph.edu"))
Depends: methods
Imports: illuminaio, minfi (>= 1.18.2), methylumi (>= 2.18.2), downloader, RCurl
Suggests: BiocStyle, RUnit, digest, knitr
Description: R interface for the The Cancer Genome Atlas (TCGA) portal to download methylation data from Illumina 27k and 450k arrays. 
